b'Mobile Suit Gundam Wing: Operation Met: b"Two video releases recapping events from the Gundam Wing TV series. Each Operation Meteor video contains an 'Odd' episode and an 'Even' episode. The episodes also featured brief new footages of the characters after the final episode of the TV series. \n\n(Source: AniDB) "
